<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Deleted</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <tr><td>{{> header}}</td></tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 32px;">
          <h1 style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 24px 0; line-height: 1.3;">Account Deleted</h1>
          <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Hello,</p>
          <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">This email confirms that your <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> account and all associated data have been permanently deleted on {{deletionDate}}.</p>
          {{#if isTrialExpired}}
          <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">Your account was deleted because your free trial ended without an active subscription.</p>
          {{else if isImmediateDeletion}}
          <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">Your account was deleted at your request.</p>
          {{else}}
          <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">Your account was deleted following your subscription cancellation and the 30-day data retention period.</p>
          {{/if}}
          <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 24px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 14px;">What was deleted:</p>
            <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
              <li>All photographs and uploaded files</li>
              <li>All rolls, collections, and galleries</li>
              <li>Person profiles and contact information</li>
              <li>Moodboards and contact sheets</li>
              <li>Account settings and preferences</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px 0;"><strong>Want to start fresh?</strong></p>
          <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">You're always welcome to create a new account and start a new free trial at any time.</p>
          <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
            <a href="{{baseUrl}}/signup" style="display: inline-block; background: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Start New Trial</a>
          </div>
          <p style="color: #999999; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 24px 0 0 0;">We hope to see you again in the future.</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr><td>{{> footer}}</td></tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
